3. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) - The paper proposes an improved partition density function to select the proper number of communities automatically, which is a topic related to data structures and algorithms. 
4. cs.SD (Software Engineering) - The paper may involve software engineering aspects such as implementation and testing of the proposed algorithm. 
5. cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) - The paper deals with network data and community detection, which can be related to networking and internet architecture research.
